The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, journalist
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, spy
2 different pets are kept: hamster, pony
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, light-blue
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, electronic
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the prince-smoker is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the dancer is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Beverage      | 7up          | milk       |
| Cigar          | blend   | prince   |
